  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hope Village of Allentown will be a community where homeless people can feel safe and secure their belongings, go to work, and live life. A place that offers addiction and mental health services to individuals who need them. Most importantly Hope Village will be a way out of the cycle of homelessness and back into being an stable and integrated member of society again. Helping the homeless community regain their empowerment, and achieve their goals, helping to their quality of life.</narrative>
  </description>
